make_securecopymagnus.sh
by greifm
requires ~/.bashrc, .securecopymagnushelp
licence GNU 3.0

# description
make_securecopymagnus creates a bash script, securecopymagnus, that eases in the arduous task of using scp
This program is specific to the molecular dynamics team at Curtin University, please feel free to change and distribute under a GNU licence

# use
To use this program execute bash make_securecopymagnus.sh
It will create .securecopymagnus.sh in your home directory using your username
It will ask if you wish to add it to your .bashrc source and act accordingly


.securecopymagnus.sh
# use
see .securecopymagnushelp